install the following packages for the proper compilation
--------------------------------------------------------
1.libfuse-dev
2.libglib2.0-dev

compilation
-----------
just type make 
#make

discription 
-----------
if the compilation is done sucsessfully you will get a file named isomount in your current directory.

testing
------
#mkdir mountpoint
#./isomount mountpoint logo.iso
the isofilesystem image will be mounted to the directory mountpoint.
